import React from 'react' function Cart({ cart, setCart, total }) { const removeToCart = (product) => { const currentBasket = cart.find(item => item.product_id === product.product_id) const basketWithoutCurrent = cart.filter(item => item.product_id !== product.product_id) currentBasket.quantity -= 1 if (currentBasket.quantity === 0) { setCart([...basketWithoutCurrent]) } else { setCart([...basketWithoutCurrent, currentBasket]) } } return ( <>
